---

Mini Vcs HOWTO:

  Checkout Vcs:
    svn co https://svn.lrde.epita.fr/svn/lrdetools/trunk/vcs

  Update your PATH:
    export PATH=$PATH:the_path_to_vcs/bin
    rehash # with zsh

  Check Vcs:
    vcs --help

  Make aliases:
    `vcs --mk-alias`

  Check the transparent mode:
    svn status!

  Commit in Olena:
    svn oln_commit 'Your news subject'
  or:
    svn olnci 'Your news subject'

